        <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
          We offer comprehensive solutions to help you build and optimize your
          sales organization.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="animate-on-scroll bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md">
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6"
          >
            1
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Sales Hiring</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            We help you identify, attract, and hire top sales talent that fits
            your company culture and goals.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="animate-on-scroll bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md"
          style={{ transitionDelay: "0.2s" }}
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6"
          >
            2
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Sales Training</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Comprehensive training programs designed to equip your team with the
            skills they need to succeed.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div
          class="animate-on-scroll bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md"
          style={{ transitionDelay: "0.4s" }}
        >
          <div
            class="w-12 h-12 bg-black text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mb-6"
          >
            3
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Performance Coaching</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700">
            Ongoing support and guidance to help your sales team develop their
            skills and exceed their targets.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12 animate-on-scroll">
        <a
          href="/services"
          class="border-2 border-black hover:bg-black hover:text-white transition-colors px-6 py-3 rounded-md text-base font-medium"
        >
          Discover More
